title: Superior Spider-Man (001 - 033 + Extras) (2013 - 2014) (digital)
description:
Superior Spider-Man (001 - 033 + Extras) (2013 - 2014) (digital) (Minutemen-Faessla)


A Marvel Now! smash hit series starring Dr. Otto Octavius as Spider-Man! This action packed series continues from the The Amazing Spider-Man #700.

SUPERIOR SPIDER-MAN KICKS OFF THE EDGE OF SPIDER-VERSE!

Extra-sized monumental issue, including a story drawn by living legend ADAM KUBERT 

How is the Superior Spider-Man still around? Where is he? What is he doing? The road to SPIDER-VERSE STARTS HERE!
